column5: I had a great time here for 2009.I hope for the same in 2010.I wish every one a happy new year esp to the admins and the ones I met.You are all great indeed and cheers to you all.Happy new year and for god sake be safe out there.by all means.cheers and happy new year to all of you on OFC.
Happy new year to you too vinni
Well here's wishing the best of health and prosperity to everyone for 2010.  Couple of fish wouldn't hurt either.
All the best to all!! Jim
